snippet.title: [OPT-OUT]: Uncanny (2021 Proof Of Concept Trailer)
snippet.description:
2024 Update:
- Video retitled to reflect how this is more accurately now an aged "Proof Of Concept".

FAQ
Is this still being made?
- Yes. Actively? No.
Why has it been on pause?
- To make time for Research.
What kind of research?
- You'll find out.
Is it still just you working on this?
- Yes and no.
How long until we see more?
- I need another year at the least.


https://optoutall.net
